Transform class that extends Action class as it can be executed as an action that is done by actor Mainly is used for Undead enemies as they can transform to PilesOfBone after first death AND BACK TO Undead enemy after 3 safety rounds of not getting hitted reaches Single Responsibility Principle as it handles only transform action in game

TravelAction - Class in game.actions
TravelAction class that extends MoveActorAction class as it can be executed as an action that is done by Player It allows player to travel between different map using GoldenFogDoor, this helps to reduce repeated code (DRY) and it also reaches Single Responsibility Principle as it handles travel action in game
